characters are determined by their status and education.
The status is determined by throwing a d6:
1-3: the character is noble
4-6: the character is from the poorer classes

The education can freely be chosen. The status determines the specifics of the education:

Educations:
Fighter:
stability:
vitality:
attunement: 0
dexterity: 5
strength: 6
charisma: 5
intelligence: 4
wisdom: 4
constitution: 6

Ranger:
stability:
vitality:
attunement: 0
dexterity: 6
strength: 5
charisma: 4
intelligence: 5
wisdom: 4
constitution: 6

Clerk:
stability:
vitality:
attunement: 4
dexterity: 4
strength: 2
charisma: 4
intelligence: 6
wisdom: 6
constitution: 4

Bard:
stability:
vitality:
attunement: 4
dexterity: 6
strength: 2
charisma: 4
intelligence: 6
wisdom: 4
constitution: 4


Special rules:
Noble:
Fighter:
lvl1: gain +2 dex when using a melee attack
lvl2: every light weapon in use of the fighter gains parry: 1d10 damage
lvl3: every medium weapon in use of the fighter gains parry: 2d6 damage


ranger:
lvl1: gain +2 dex when using a ranged attack
lvl2: gain a +1 bonus when returning to stealth from a stealth attack
lvl3: gain a +1 bonus when parrying

clerk:
lvl1: gain the spells heal, magic hand and -2 dex, +2 char
lvl2: gain the spells lesser heal, light
lvl3: gain the spells soul arrow, soul spear

bard:
lvl1: gain the spell inspire and -2 dex, +2 char
lvl2: gain the spells lesser heal, mockery
lvl3: gain the spell fire ball



poor:
Fighter:
lvl1: gain +2 str when using a melee attack
lvl2: every light weapon does 1d4 more damage
lvl3: every medium weapon does 1d6 more damage


ranger:
lvl1: gain +2 dex when using sleight of hand
lvl2: gain a +1 bonus when returning to stealth from a stealth attack
lvl3: gain a +2 bonus when dodging

clerk:
lvl1: gain the spells heal, magic hand and a +1 bonus when using stealth
lvl2: gain the spells lesser heal, light
lvl3: gain the spells soul arrow, soul spear

bard:
lvl1: gain the spell inspire and a +1 bonus when using stealth
lvl2: gain the spells lesser heal, mockery
lvl3: gain the spell fire ball